items.text:
🎬 CASTING CALL – FALLING LEAVES 🍂
We’re making an indie LGBTQ+ romance feature in Birmingham this autumn and we’re looking for talent!

✨ Roles:
-Jess (early 20s- Female) – Skater chick. Bold, witty, restless. Skateboarding skills are a plus.
-Alex (late 20s- Female) – Polished, articulate, book-lover. Smart & thoughtful.

-Ryan (20s, male/female)-Jess’s skatepark mate. Cheerful, loud, comic relief.
-Blake  (20s, Masc, female-identifying)-Jess’s best friend. Sharp-tongued, supportive but blunt.
-Margaret (late 20s/ early 30s, female-identifying)-Alex’s sister. Pragmatic, grounded, voice of reason.

📍 Filming in Birmingham
📅 Dates: October to Early November 
💌 Apply: FallingLeavesFilm@gmail.com – send headshot (not professional), autobiography.

🏳️‍🌈We encourage applications from LGBTQ+ actors & underrepresented voices.
Let’s bring this love story to life. 💕

#CastingCall #FallingLeavesFilm #LGBTQFilm #BirminghamFilm #IndieCinema

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'When chaos and order collide, love takes root. FALLING LEAVES ลุคเาพ'

topComments.text: I would be happy to play the role of Alex! I'm bisexual, and have a passion for acting :)
Hello, that sounds like wind to my ears. Short question: are actors from germany welcome too?

# 🎬 **NAGRANIA KRAKÓW **🎬

Do realizacji ciekawego filmu na jeden z największych kanałów YouTube w Polsce poszukujemy osoby chętnej wziąć udział w projekcie. Zadaniem aktora będzie odegranie krótkiej sceny z elementami improwizacji. 
## 🔎 **Kogo szukamy?**
* Mężczyzna w wieku 25-50 lat
* Łysa głowa (nie wymagana, ale mile widziana 🙂)
* Dystans do siebie
* Swoboda przed kamerą (doświadczenie mile widziane, ale niekonieczne)
## ℹ️ **INFORMACJE**
* Lokalizacja: Kraków
* Termin: 17.09.25
* Czas trwania: 1 godzina

** Jesteś chętny? – odezwij się w wiadomości prywatnej, a prześlę więcej szczegółów! **

Hi all, my name is Reuben Carnaby, a student of Film and Television at the University of South Australia. I'm directing our final project in my graduating year, and am looking for anybody interested to be in my film as an extra.

Shooting will be the morning/afternoon of Sunday September 28th.

If interested, please email me at:

reubencarnaby@gmail.com

Or, feel free to shoot me a message!

Thank you,
Reuben

items.text:
ISO MALE CONTORTIONIST FOR INDEPENDENT FEATURE FILM

A new independent production company, Tu Bruja Productions, is looking for a male contortionist to join the cast of our upcoming project, “The Return,” and we would love to source local talent as much as possible. It’s a psychological thriller, incorporating supernatural elements, and we need a tall male contortionist for some of the spookier bits. The shoot is scheduled for 10/12 for an 18 to 21-day shoot in the Wilmington, NC area, but they would only need to be on set for a day or two. This is a paid opportunity where the rate can be discussed.

If you’re interested, please email [vvicenty@tubrujaproductions.com](mailto:vvicenty@tubrujaproductions.com) with your resume, reel, and working contact number. Please don’t DM, as I can’t read message requests. Thanks in advance!

#paidopportunity #ISO #contortionist #contortinists #filmcast #MovieCasting

items.text:
Hi Everyone!

Sharing from Bryar Casting, in case you haven’t heard yet, **The Reality Directory** is a fresh casting platform connecting real people with amazing opportunities in reality TV, documentaries, commercials looking for everyday folks with incredible stories!

Whether you’re outgoing, quirky, or just your authentic self, this is your chance to be discovered by casting producers looking for people just like you.

Memberships start at $14.99/month. If you’re keen to join or want to learn more, check it out here: www.therealitydirectory.com

And to help you get started, DM us @therealitydirectory with the code **FOUND** for an exclusive discount!

Got questions? Feel free to reach out at casting@therealitydirectory.com or tag friends who might be interested — we’d love to welcome you to the community!

I’m now offering private professional career guidance for actors/models/voice actors. I will help you navigate through the industry while providing honest and constructive feedback. Helping you build the perfect package to grab the attention of agents, and recommend the best agents to reach out to. I will review all of your materials and help you with creating your reel/clips, choosing your best headshots, laying out your resume, and writing a great introduction. Picking the best images and photographers for your modeling portfolio. Making sure you have your best runway walk and poses. Selecting the best copy for your monologues and VO commercial reels. And helping you pick the best acting class/coach for you. 

I work with all levels of talent. Beginners, children, teens, adults, as well as established talent. We will focus on everything you need/want to focus on. This session is for you!

Please email me for 30/60 minute private professional session rates and special promotions!

items.text:
PEDOFIL WCIĄŻ AKTYWNY!!!
Uwaga zwłaszcza na to konto.

Osoba, która na przestrzeni miesięcy posługuje się kontem, które wciąż znajduje się pod linkiem https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61571091669955, nadal jest aktywna. Przedstawia się jako Marcelina Marcelina, Marcelina Gajda, a wcześniej Katarzyna Kw.

Pedofil ten działa obecnie na zasadzie książki telefonicznej, czyli pisze do osób z grupy, które będą w jego „guście”. Zaznaczę też, że nie ma go na grupach, gdzie jesteśmy razem z Maciej Brożek .

Głównie i w ogromnej części przypadków, celuje w dziewczynki. Potrafi jednak też zaszantażować swoje ofiary skłaniając, czy też raczej zmuszając je do dalszej „współpracy”.

Powołuje się na kontakty w Netflix Polska, TVN itd. Tutaj muszę wspomnieć, że ani Netflix, ani TVN nie rozmawiają o angażach tylko z dziećmi, lub w ogóle tylko i wyłącznie z osobami niepełnoletnimi. Osobnik ten jest jednak przebiegły i rozmawiając z rodzicem, potrafi nawiązać na równi kontakt z dzieckiem. Oczekuje wtedy wysłania tak jak we wszystkich wcześniejszych przypadkach, zdjęć w bieliźnie, a później nagich, gdyż tego wymaga „rola”.

Drogie Grupowiczki! Drodzy Grupowicze! Żadna stacja TV lub agencja, czy też firma nie będą oczekiwały od Was nagich zdjęć. Gdyby ktoś Was o nie poprosił, to nie róbcie z tego tajemnicy przede mną, a już na pewno też i przed Waszymi rodzicami. Pamiętajcie, że gwarantuję anonimowość.

Po szczegóły zapraszam na grupę https://www.facebook.com/groups/1271416653748731/.

Poniżej przedstawiam kilka zrzutów z jego fejkowych profili. W komentarzu jest także link do jego konta, gdyż przeglądarka FB nie zawsze wyświetla link z poziomu treści postu.

#pedofil #nagiezdjęcia #netflixpolska #rolawnetflixie #nudesy

items.text:
‼️ Casting Call ‼️

​

Für einen Werbespot suchen wir 2 männliche Darsteller 🎬

​

Rollen:

25–35 Jahre, vorzugsweise dunkle Haare, Muttersprache Deutsch

40–50 Jahre, vorzugsweise dunkle Haare, Muttersprache Deutsch

​

📅 Drehtermin: 22. oder 23.09.2025 (nur 1 Tag, aber bitte beide Tage verfügbar sein)

💶 Gage: 669 € pauschal pro Person

✈️ Reisekosten: werden komplett übernommen

📍 Drehort: Kopenhagen

​

👉 Kommentiere mit ❤️ und du erhältst den Bewerbungslink!

Nach deiner Anmeldung bekommst du automatisch eine Mail, in der wir weitere Infos von dir abfragen (bitte ggf. auch im Spam nachsehen!).

​

Bitte bewirb dich nur, wenn du an den genannten Tagen verfügbar bist.

​

Wir freuen uns auf euch!

Dein Castfinder-Team ✨

items.text:
🎬 CASTING: Familie søges til reklamefilm 🌟 Lønnet 

Vi leder efter en skandinavisk mand og kvinde i slut 30’erne/start 40’erne samt en pige på 7–8 år til en varm og troværdig reklameproduktion for en detailkæde. Gerne søges som en samlet familie, men ikke nødvendigt 

📍 Optagelse: cirka 4 timer 
Lokation: Herning  
📅 Dato: 7 oktober 
🎥 Brug: Sociale medier, TV, biograf og online i Danmark, Sverige, Norge og Finland
🖼️ Stillbilleder: Bruges online og evt. på print i kædens fysiske butikker
⏳ Brugsret: 3 år med mulighed for forlængelse (brugen af reklamen er dog sæson præget, så ville i vintermånederne) 

Udstråling: Glad og frisk udstråling, og med evnen til at skabehygge.
Samspillet mellem de to voksne og datteren er bærende, og det er derfor vigtigt at de voksne er gode med børn og at barnet er skuespils vant.

📩 Interesseret? Send et par billeder + kort præsentation eller materiale fra tidligere projekter til [sille.schnoor13@gmail.com]
Skriv gerne “Familie casting” i emnefeltet.

items.text:
Casting Call – Mandlig skuespiller/statist søges

Vi er et hold på seks studerende fra VIA Film & Transmedia i Aarhus. I forbindelse med et skoleprojekt samarbejder vi med designer Fie Nielsen og hendes studie, Fjör Studio, om branding af en ny tøjkollektion.

Kollektionen udforsker, hvad det vil sige at være mand i dag, og leger med udtryk, der udfordrer de traditionelle forestillinger om styrke, følelser og identitet.

Vi søger en mand i alderen 17–30 år, ca. 180 cm høj, almindelig af bygning og med tøjstørrelse small–medium.

Praktisk info
 Optagelserne finder sted i Skanderborg
 Mandag den 22/9
 Kl. 09.00–17.00

Projektet er frivilligt, men vi sørger selvfølgelig for mad, drikke, transport – og en sjov oplevelse samt muligheden for at få et spændende projekt på CV’et.

Kontakt Fredrik på (+45) 2285 1519 eller 354549@via.dk, hvis du er interesseret. 

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig!

items.text:
Hej 

Mit navn er Luca Giusio 
Jeg er 17 år 
Og bor i Kolding/vejle 

Jeg laver lige det her opslag fordi jeg rigtig gerne vil være skuespiller og elsker det med film og skuespil og alt i den dur 
Jeg er en passioneret og energisk person, der elsker at udtrykke mig gennem både drama og humor. 

Jeg har erfaring med:

Har været en del af dystopia i Vejle siden 2020
Har gået til teater i 2 år og været med i 2 forestillinger 
Har lavet små kortfilm og min egen spillefilm igennem min barndom 

Højde: 175
Sprog: Dansk/engelsk 
Jeg er dedikeret lærenem – og så elsker jeg at arbejde kreativt sammen med andre

Tak for at I tager jer tid til at læse med 

jeg håber at høre fra jer

Bedste hilsner Luca Giusio

items.text:
🎄 Now Recruiting: Christmas Elves – Solihull Grotto 🎄

This isn’t a shopping centre gig – this is the real North Pole magic.

We’re searching for brilliant, bold, and quick-thinking Christmas Elves to join our immersive, theatrical grotto experience in Solihull this December.

This isn’t a mall grotto with plastic tinsel and awkward photos – it’s a full-on magical Christmas adventure, where families step into Santa’s world and leave believing in the magic.

⸻

✨ About the Role:

As one of Santa’s official North Pole Elves, you’ll be:
🎁 Meeting and guiding families through the experience
🎁 Interacting in character with Mr & Mrs Claus
🎁 Keeping the energy high and the story flowing
🎁 Delivering top-tier improv and engaging with children and adults alike
🎁 Creating unforgettable festive memories

⸻

🎭 What We’re Looking For:
 • Confident performers with strong improvisation skills
 • Able to stay in character and think on your feet
 • Warm, playful, and genuinely enthusiastic
 • Reliable and professional – with a passion for Christmas magic

Auditions (including an improv section) will be held in October.

⸻

📅 Must be available ALL of the following dates:
 • 30th November (Soft Opening)
 • 6th & 7th December
 • 13th & 14th December
 • 20th & 21st December

💷 Pay: £175 per day
🎽 Costume: Provided – you just bring the sparkle
📍 Location: Solihull (non-mall venue – truly immersive setting on a Christmas Tree Farm)

⸻

If you love Christmas, live for laughter, and can keep the magic alive all day long, we want to hear from you!

🎅 Apply Now:

Complete the below link

https://forms.cloud.microsoft/e/Zyik7tkK4L

Closing date September 30th or when we find the right team.

Join the magic. Be the Elf they’ll never forget.

items.text:
Lone Riders Casting Episode 1 1.2

We need to fill some heads before we start filming so get those auditions in ASAP. Please

Lone Riders is a new original series created by Myself and Leo Henry. This casting is for the pilot episode this year before working on four more next year. The project will be taking place in Kirkcaldy Fife and the surrounding area. If you can travel petrol money will be paid for and food/beverage will be provided (please let any allergy preferences be known before hand) The filming will take place around October 2025. With specific dates to be worked out. 

Soldier 2 & 3 (Playing Age 30-40) Random Soldiers who get killed at the beginning. M

SOLDIER 3
I know, from what that guy at the base was saying, I expected more.

SOLDIER 3
It will almost be a pleasure to dispose of the great…Lone Rider.

Beta 2 (Playing Age 20-25) Beta 2 is the youngest of the Betas. F

Hey cut the chit chat, the leader is coming.

Beta 5,6 &7 (Playing Age 20-40) The Betas are one note characters but follow direct orders. M or F

BETA 7
Can’t believe we’ve been dragged out into the middle of nowhere just to hunt down two thieves. 

BETA 5
Cut the Captain some slack. We've been specially chosen for this task.

BETA 6
Sir what about Patient 0.

Please send all auditions either to cjnicoll476@gmail.com or DM me.

Crew Casting
We would like to bring on a fly on the wall documentary filmmaker. The responsibility would be to film interviews and general live footage. Your contribution to the project would not go unnoticed. 
Camera operator

I know, from what that guy at the base was saying, I expected more.

It will almost be a pleasure to dispose of the great…Lone Rider.

Yes, it is correct and acceptable to refer to a person from India as "Indian," and this is distinct from the term "Native American Indian" or "American Indian" which refers to Indigenous people of the Americas. While the word "Indian" as a reference to people from India is not offensive, using it for Indigenous peoples of the Americas is a misnomer that originated from Christopher Columbus's historical mistake. To be precise, it's best to specify "Indian" for someone from India and "Native American" or another preferred term for Indigenous peoples of the Americas.

'CUT PRICE' - The date is set for another ‘Songwriting Weekend Workshop’ (Saturday 11th and Sunday 12th October 2025 - 9.30 am to 5.30 pm both days). 

Whether you are a budding songwriter, a wordsmith, poet, or just someone interested in doing something creatively satisfying and different to escape the endless noise of an insane world we live in today, then this is for you.

With the emphasis on how to work intuitively in your storytelling, lyric writing, rhythm awareness and top line melodies. 

We will be joined by the hit songwriter of multiple Rod Stewart hits and legendary guitarist in Rod's band, Mr Jim Cregan.

Jim will take part in a Question & Answer discussion on how he co-wrote those classic hits and how he added his legendary guitar magic and compositional skills to countless other artist’s albums over the years. If you are nice to him he may well join you hands-on with your efforts over the weekend workshop.

There will be a full buffet lunch as well as refreshments over both days - the camaraderie of participants will carry on during the evenings over drinks and dinner in the local hostellerie too. 

The ticket price for the whole weekend has been slashed to a mere  £250 and that also guarantees that our mentorship extends far into your creative future too.

Interested?  

Please email for full details : info@foskettsfolkfactory.com 

With all good Wishes

Charley Foskett

items.text:
Hello all! I am 20 years old and I’m hoping to begin on proper journey of working and hopefully being casted in roles for pretty much anything! I don’t know how I can go about this! 

My only experience is college and GCSE Drama, currently in level 3 performing and production arts, I have acted in a wide range of characters but I don’t have much to show for it. I’m an alternative person and I don’t yet have any professional headshots so I’m looking for anyone who’d be willing to give me a chance .

This is me and I hope that someone knows a show that would be interested in my unique style. Thankyou so much !

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of 1 person
May be an image of 1 person

topComments.text:
Clear headshots needed. Best professional but a friend could take them for you Neutral background natural pose ( one only with any piercings) 
Casting want to see a basic you 
Google Spotlight criteria 
Look for opportunities to get little bits of film  ( student ones don’t usually pay ) 
These create material for a showreel
Get paid work which you can apply to Spotlight with

Your longer-term objective should be to qualify for Spotlight. Getting there will involve either training at a recognised institution, such as a drama school, or building up a little bit of professional experience. You can join sites such as Mandy, Backstage or Casting Callback to start applying for acting jobs, albeit the vast majority will be jobs at the lower end of the ladder. You will need half-decent headshots, though you needn't spend a fortune at this point. It would also be useful to put up a self-tape of you acting, preferably in a dialogue scene. There's plenty of advice online about setting up a basic self-tape, and most modern phones have a good enough camera and mic. Ask an actor friend to read the other character but keep them out of the shot, so we can focus on YOU. Find some acting classes near you as well; you'll need to train your skills. Being 'alternative' isn't an issue: if you're good enough and work hard enough, then you've got as much chance as the next hopeful 20 year-old. Don't worry about agents at this point; there's time for that a few years down the line. Agents will only take an interest once you've got the foundations of a career built up; they only make money if YOU make money from acting. They're not there to 'give people a chance', they make business decisions. NEVER pay to join an agency, however they try to justify the fees. I recommend getting a copy of the Actors and Performers Yearbook, which your local library might have, or could order for you. That will give you an overview into how the UK industry functions. Your college should be advising you about this stuff as well. Have you spoken to your teachers? Presumably a few of them have some professional experience...

items.text: Zapraszam do skorzystania z mojej oferty: mentoring aktorski, nagranie wizytówek oraz montaż demo aktorskiego 🎬🤩

sharedPost.text:
Chcesz zostać aktorką/aktorem albo mieć więcej aktorskiej pracy ale nie wiesz co konkretnie zrobić? 🤔 Jeżeli tak - zapraszam na konsultacje do mnie, nagranie wizytówek i montaż demo aktorskiego! 🎬🤩 Szczegóły w opisie! 

🎥 Mentoring aktorski 

Dla kogo? 

Dla każdego kto chce pracować jako aktor/aktorka na planach zdjęciowych. Zarówno dla tych bez doświadczenia, któryórzy nie wiedzą jak zacząć i co zrobić jak i dla tych co już pierwsze kroki mają za sobą ale chcieliby mieć więcej pracy i potrzebują rady w tym zakresie 🙂 

Na czym polega? 

Spotkanie ze mną 1:1 online, trwające godzinę. Opowiesz mi jakie zlecenia aktorskie Cię interesują - czyli Twój aktorski cel i według tego dobieramy odpowiedni plan działania. Jeżeli masz materiały aktorskie - to je omówimy i powiem co warto byłoby jeszcze do nich dodać lub jak je “podrasować”. Jeżeli nie masz to dowiesz się co i jak masz zrobić żeby je mieć 🙂 Powiem o moich poleceniach agencji aktorskich, jak samodzielnie i łatwo zrobić demo, jak nagrać i co powiedzieć w wizytówkach, jak samodzielnie szukać pracy, jak się wyceniać, na co uważać. I odpowiem na wszystkie inne Twoje pytania. Po spotkaniu otrzymasz ode mnie maila z planem działania i priorytetami do wykonania + materiałami pomocniczymi dot. materiałów aktorskich. 

🎥 Coaching aktorski z wizytówki + nagranie wizytówek w studio 

Na czym polega? 

✅ Tworzę tekst do wizytówek na podstawie informacji o Twoim doświadczeniu, pasjach, zainteresowaniach, który dostajesz przed nagraniem według castingowych wytycznych, który pokaże Twoje największe atuty

✅W studio nagrań nagrywamy 3-4 wizytówki:

🎬 do filmów i seriali 
🎬 do reklam w wersji dłuższej 
🎬 do reklam w wersji krótszej 
🎬 w języku obcym 
Ewentualnie możemy dograć wizytówkę modelingową 

✅ W trakcie nagrywania zadbam o Twoje rozluźnienie, dobrą atmosferę oraz zrobimy kilka ćwiczeń które pomogą pokazać na wizytówkach Twoją energię i błysk w oku 
oraz będę czuwać nad całym procesem

✅ Wizytówki nagramy według aktualnych standardów i wymogów castingowych 

✅ Dostaniesz zmontowane wizytówki gotowe do wysłania przez WeTransfer

🎥 Demo aktorskie 

montaż demo aktorskiego + konsultacja 

Na czym polega? 

✅ otrzymasz ode mnie demo aktorskie zmontowane zgodnie z obecnymi wymogami reżyserów castingu + podczas konsultacji wspólnie dobierzemy sceny, które się w nim znajdą oraz przedstawię Ci mój pomysł na ich kolejność 

Podczas konsultacji dowiesz się również:

✅ jak pobierać materiały do demo aktorskiego 
✅ jakie są obecne wymogi i standardy wzgledem aktorskiego demo 
✅ jakie sceny wybierać i w jakiej kolejności je zmontować  
✅ jak samemu w łatwy sposób przemontować demo pod konkretny casting

From the creators of the viral horror short “The Forever Home” (Fear Tapes on Instagram), now adapted into a feature-length indie film set for theatrical and streaming release.

📍 Filming Location: Los Angeles, CA

📅 Filming Dates: November 2025 (4-day shoot)

💀 Genre: Horror (1980s period piece)

About the Film:

The Forever Home is a chilling feature set in the 1980s, following a haunted foster home plagued by the presence of its caretaker and six ghostly children. The short film has already built a large following online and this feature is expected to gain major exposure upon release.

Casting Roles:

6 Children (ages 8–12) – Any gender, any ethnicity

Non-speaking roles (portraying ghost children)

No prior acting experience required — ability to follow direction and stay in character is key

Compensation:

Non-union, unpaid

Meals, snacks, and drinks provided during filming days

IMDb/film credits + valuable experience on a professional horror set

Why Join:

This is a unique opportunity to be part of an indie horror film already generating industry buzz. The short film this project is based on has a strong cult following, and this feature is expected to reach theaters and major streaming platforms. Perfect for child actors and newcomers looking to build experience and get their name out there.

To Submit:

📧 Email nickcooper.feartapes@gmail.com with the subject line: FOREVER HOME – Child Casting

Include:

Child’s name, age, and recent photo (headshot or clear candid)

Parent/guardian name and contact info

Any previous acting experience (not required)

Für meinen historisch-romantischen Kurzfilm (1–3 Minuten) suche ich eine Schauspielpartnerin (25–30 Jahre) aus Ulm oder Umgebung.

Über das Projekt:
Es handelt sich um ein Herzensprojekt, nicht bezahlt, dafür mit viel Leidenschaft. Wir drehen eine Szene im Stil klassischer Historienromanzen – Spaziergang, Dialoge voller Tiefe, ein erster Kuss und eine leidenschaftliche Kaminszene.

Wichtig:

Keine Scheu oder Scham vor einem Kuss und einer leidenschaftlichen Szene (ästhetisch, stilvoll, keine Nacktheit).

Du musst keine ausgebildete Schauspielerin sein – entscheidend ist deine Spielfreude, Leidenschaft und der Mut, dich auf die Rolle einzulassen.

Wir bieten:

Ein kleines, motiviertes Team

Eine professionelle Umsetzung mit viel Herzblut

Material für dein Showreel

Eine intensive Erfahrung voller Romantik und Leidenschaft

📩 Wenn du Lust hast, Teil dieses Projekts zu werden, melde dich bitte mit einer kurzen Nachricht und Foto.

✨ Lass uns gemeinsam eine Szene erschaffen, die Romantik und Leidenschaft lebendig macht! ✨

*One night, one place, one past, two people.*

*Female, 22-26, African-American*

*A sharp, ambitious med student is forced to confront old wounds when the man who broke her heart shows up at her door, bleeding and in need.*

## *Christian*

*A charming but reckless gangster trying to turn his life around in hopes of a second chance with his lost love.*

*Please submit a self-tape with a couple of different takes.*

**If you have any questions, please contact me at jenmcfar3@gmail.com**

**PAID OPPORTUNITY – Origin**

📢 Have you lived through a moment that completely changed your life?

We’re creating a brand-new podcast for Origin, the platform where **women share their most intimate, powerful, and unforgettable real-life experiences.**

We’re looking for women with extraordinary true stories: medical challenges, romantic relationships, family conflict, and those raw moments that transformed your life. If your experience has stayed with you, and you believe it could move or inspire others, we’d be honored to hear it.

🎥 This is a** paid opportunity** and filming happens in a** London** studio.

If that sounds like you (or someone you know), get in touch!

📧 Send your story to **[mireille.lee@upstream-media.co.uk](mailto:mireille.lee@upstream-media.co.uk)**

https://www.youtube.com/@_origin

The demand for the infamous Huntrix Trio from Kpop Demon Hunters has been skyrocketing! We’re receiving double and triple bookings for Huntrix themed children’s birthday parties and special events, so we are now seeking additional character performers to join our team! 

🎭 Roles: Mira, Zoey, and Rumi 

📌 Requirements:
 • Must be comfortable performing in character and interacting with kids
 • Resemblance to the characters is preferred. We welcome applicants of all ethnic backgrounds—if your look matches the style of the cartoons or live-action idols, we encourage you to apply!
 • Flexible weekend availability 

Interested? ✨
📩 DM us or text (719) 246-7591 for more information!

Come be part of the dream team and bring the Huntrix girls to life for kids and fans who can’t wait to meet them! 💜⚔️🎶

Hallo, für meinen studentischen, dokumentarischen Kurzfilm suche ich passende Filmmusik, es geht um eine Kneipe.

Budget kann ich nicht anbieten. Aber natürlich Erwähnung im Film.
Der Film wird in einem Berliner Kino laufen zur Premiere und wenn es gut läuft auf Festivals und in weiteren Arthousekinos.

Wer daran interessiert ist gerne mit Link zur Musik kommentieren.

Liebe Grüße aus Berlin

topComments.text:
Der Film soll in Kinos und auf Festivals laufen, dafür bezahlen die Besucher bestimmt auch Eintritt.
Sprich: Einnahmen sind dann da.
Warum kann dann kein Budget für die Filmmusik bezahlt werden?
Sollte ich mit meiner Vermutung daneben liegen, klär mich auf. Danke.

items.text:
Rainhill Garrick Society are performing ‘ Habeus Corpus’ by Alan Bennett on February 12th-14th 2026.

Alan Bennett’s Habeus Corpus is set in the Seventies and follows the lives of the Wicksteed family. The story follows Dr and Muriel Wicksteed as they both seek pleasure and fun outside of their marital relationship. The farcical play is very fast paced, incredibly funny and occasionally surreal. The bumbling sex-obsessed British characters such as the virginal vicar, the ﬂat chested spinster, the peering doctor, his frustrated wife and of course a bra salesman man all come together in this bizarre and thoroughly entertaining story.

Parts available:-

Dennis Wicksteed - the hypochondriac son of Dr Wickseed, (20-30)

Felicity Rumpers - young, nubile, upper class  (20-30)

Constance Wicksteed - the sister of Dr Wicksteed, flat chested and sex starved, (20+) 

Play read through Tuesday 21st October at 7.30 in Rainhill Village Hall
Auditions- Thursday 23rd October at 7.30 Rainhill Village Hall 
Rehearsals are on Tuesdays and Thursday evenings 7.30-9.30 and the 3 Sundays prior to the performance.
Audition pieces are available on request. 

We are an amateur group so the roles are unpaid, but we are a well respected group of 83 years standing who enjoy great support from a large dedicated audience. 
The play is great fun with some slapstick and music but with some poignant moments that say a lot about relationships.

For more information, please email: sophiebrogan99@gmail.com

Hi everyone,
I’m Callum Foley 24, an actor based in Nottingham. I’ve recently been working on background and student film projects, and I’m keen to get involved in short films, indie projects, and commercials to build on-screen experience.

I’m currently training at Nottingham Actors Workshop and working towards joining **Spotlight**, so I’m looking to create footage that will form my first professional showreel.

I have professional headshots available and would be happy to send them over if you have a role I could be suitable for. I’m based in Nottingham but happy to travel for projects.

You can reach me at **callumfoley1000@gmail.com**.

Thanks,

Hey guys, I'm running a taster session for the screen acting class this Friday for only a fiver! 

In the session, you'll get to practice on a given scene over a couple of takes and I'll also go through the three programs of this autumn: 
* Screen acting drop-in 
* Screen acting Monthly workshop (over 4weeks) to develop presence and get confident on camera. 
* The directing actors Workshop with the last monday of each month with actors in the room! 
* More info at interactors.co.uk @ : info.interactors@gmail.com Make sure you book the ticket for friday via the website if you wish to come! Looking forward to seeing you there!  whttps://www.instagram.com/p/DOeaxfCDLI_/?igsh=MWU0ZHg5aGh5cmI0OQ==

Are you 18-25? Do you find yourself talking more to ChatGPT than real people? Struggling to make new friends? We want to hear from you!

We are casting for a new documentary about the loneliness crisis in the UK and I’m looking for contributors from Manchester (and close surrounding areas) who are (or have) experienced loneliness and would be willing to share their personal story.

Please drop Olivia an email on [oliviaryan.talent@gmail.com](mailto:oliviaryan.talent@gmail.com) with the subject line DOC OP.

Please attach an image of yourself, your age, where you are from. and a couple of sentences briefly sharing your story.

📣SHEFFIELD PROFIT-SHARE ACTING OPPORTUNITY📣

'Quiet in the Wings' by Rurik Seven

Dennis Le'Claire, 'World's Greatest Actor', is missing - and it's opening night! It's a theatre production's worst nightmare, that is until Sebastian Paris, 'World's Greatest Understudy', arrives on the scene to save the day. But all is not as it seems, as talks of foul play begin to spread.

In this force of farce, take a peek behind the curtain at scheming stage hands, devious directors, and preposterous playwrights.

Audition information:
🗓️ Mon 22 (18.30-20.30), Sat 27 (14.30-16.30) September
📍 Sharrow Community Forum
📽️ Self tapes accepted
🔗 for audition sign up and more information, including rehearsals, show dates, and characters: https://forms.gle/Mw5Z7eJwtAY8wwMy9

items.summary:
📣SHEFFIELD PROFIT-SHARE ACTING OPPORTUNITY📣

'Quiet in the Wings' by Rurik Seven

Dennis Le'Claire, 'World's Greatest Actor', is missing - and it's opening night! It's a theatre production's worst nightmare, that is until Sebastian Paris, 'World's Greatest Understudy', arrives on the scene to save the day. But all is not as it seems, as talks of foul play begin to spread.

In this force of farce, take a peek behind the curtain at scheming stage hands, devious directors, and preposterous playwrights.

Audition information:
🗓️ Mon 22 (18.30-20.30), Sat 27 (14.30-16.30) September
📍 Sharrow Community Forum
📽️ Self tapes accepted
🔗 for audition sign up and more information, including rehearsals, show dates, and characters: https://forms.gle/Mw5Z7eJwtAY8wwMy9

items.text:
Rob and I are excited to offer another On Camera Experience for the fall!

6 Classes
October 7th - November 11th 
Tuesdays, 6:30 PM until roughly 9:30 PM
$475 per person (that’s only $80 per class!)

Class Outline
Class One: Getting to know each other, on camera terms and techniques
Class Two: Commercials
Class Three: Comedy
Class Four: Drama
Class Five: Video Games
Class Six: “On Set” - a professional camera op will be filming this class. 

Classes will be a mix of on-camera acting technique and scene study with some acting feedback. All raw footage will be filmed and shared with the students. 

Must join by Tuesday, September 30th.  SPACE IS LIMITED!! To reserve a spot, please contact Sylvia at sylvia@sylviagregorycasting.com

Hope you can be a part of it!

items.text:
Casting Call (Non-Union) Paid

Looking for actors to play the role of a client in a simulated therapy session. The video clips will be used in an online training system for counselors and psychologists. The sessions are generally improvised with some prompts or loose scripting.

All ages, all gender expressions/identities, all ethnicities, and persons with disabilities are welcome. We are also very interested in filming with queer couples, interracial couples, or polycules.

Comfortable English fluency is required.

Immediate filming dates are September 23 through 26, but more will occur in the future so please submit if you're interested at all.

Location is downtown Vancouver - Gastown. Pay is 60 cad, duration: 1 hour

Please email phil@skillsetter.com with your headshot and resume. If you've submitted for a past session, you're welcome to submit again.

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of text that says 'Skillse Skillsetter'

topComments.text: My daughter did it once and pay was $400…. Is that still the same for kids?
Emailed! :)

items.text:
**Casting Call - Supporting Characters**

Project: Midnight Snack, for Vancouver Chinese Film Festival

Volunteer, non-union, lunch provided, IMDb credit provided.

Location: Vancouver, British Columbia.

Shoot Date: September 28, 2025

Role: Asian Thug (Male, 30–40s)

Bitter, confrontational, menacing — anger barely concealing shame.

Role: Asian Drunk Man (Male, 40–50s)

Checked-out and disheveled — apathetic and broken down.

Role: The Clerk (Male, 60s–80s)

An Old Asian man, a quiet, trembling man working late — the embodiment of a worn-out future.

Submit headshots to teammidnightsnack@gmail.com

topComments.text: Do you need to speak Chinese for these roles?  Thanks
Pay… don’t be a crook

sharedPost.text:
We are casting for a role in our feature film ‘Fairy Dust’!

Please only apply if you fit the brief in the picture and also meet the following criteria:
- Actors must be North Wales based.
- Actors must have the right to work in the UK.
- Actors must be over the age of 18 in real life.
- Must be comfortable wearing full face mask.

Pay is £100 for the day.
Local travel expenses will also be covered & lunch provided.

To apply please send your Spotlight link (or acting CV) as well as your showreel to momentsoffiction@outlook.com

.

media.ocrText: May be an image of text that says 'CASTING CALL ARTHUR Age 18-50 Local actors only please! Filming near Llanberis, North Wales Date: Weds 8th October "A pair of brigands-- brigands--ARTHUR -ARTHUR and EMIL, dressed like heavy metal bikers in devil masks. Drunk. Belligerent." Movement role as you'll playing the body but not the voice. Will still need to know the lines for the purpose of acting out the scenes. Please read the caption for more details andfor apply.'

message.text:
🔥 No son reliquias. No es pasado.
Es fuerza, ritmo y energía que siguen latiendo.
Lo que hacemos no es una pieza de museo. Es danza viva.

Tomamos la fuerza del gaucho —su energía, su destreza, su presencia—
y la llevamos a un escenario con una propuesta estética cuidada y contemporánea.

💥 Que suenen los bombos, que vibren las boleadoras, que estalle la danza.
@millennialgaucho.ok 

#danza #malambo #boleadoras #latigos #argentina

Hey, ich brauche eure Hilfe!

Suche eine Schauspielerin im Alter zwischen 30 bis 35, du solltest nicht größer sein als 1.68 und eine sportliche Figur haben.
Du solltest wenn möglich aus der Region Dresden/Niederlausitz kommen.
Die Gage ist selbstverständlich.
Bei Interesse oder für weitere Infos bitte melden.

Ich habe den größten Fehler meines Lebens gemacht und jemanden der mir sehr am Herzen liegt sehr verletzt und möchte damit diesen Fehler aus der Welt schaffen.

items.text:
**CASTING-AUFRUF – UGC-Videodreh für Immobilienprojekt in Heidelberg // Donnerstag 25.09.2025**
 
Drehort: Heidelberg // Bahnstadt

Drehtag: 25.09.2025 - 10.00 Uhr
 
Geplanter Drehzeitraum: halber Drehtag (4–5 Stunden)
Schauspielhonorar: 500 € pauschal
Was wir drehen:

Für unseren Kunden, einen Immobilienunternehmen aus Hamburg, produzieren wir 25 kurze UGC-Videos (User Generated Content) für Social Media & Online-Ads. Die Videos sind authentisch gesprochene Clips, die direkt in die Kamera eingesprochen werden – klar, sympathisch, ruhig.

Skriptlänge pro Video: 40–60 Sekunden, ein Teleprompter ist vor Ort – keine Auswendiglernerei notwendig.
 
Gesucht werden:
* 1 Schauspielerin & 1 Schauspieler
* Alter: 28–40 Jahre
* Look: authentisch, gepflegt, urban-professionell – ein natürlicher „Young Professional“-Vibe (Think: Start-up, Immobilienberater, Creator mit Vertrauensausstrahlung)
* Sprache: Hochdeutsch, sichere Sprechweise, gute Artikulation
* Erfahrung mit Kamera & Social Media Ads von Vorteil, aber keine Voraussetzung
Über uns:

Wir sind die IMMO 4.0 GmbH, ein Performance-Marketing-Unternehmen aus Heidelberg.

Wir entwickeln Marketingkampagnen für Immobilienvertriebe, Bauträger und Kapitalanlageprodukte im DACH-Raum – und setzen dabei bewusst auf echtes, greifbares Storytelling mit professionellem UGC-Content.

Das bieten wir Dir:
* 500 € Pauschalgage
* Teleprompter + eingespielte Crew vor Ort
* Styling & Text-Input durch uns (kein Kostüm notwendig, clean/professionell reicht)
* Reelfähige Referenz für Deine Mappe
* Zusammenarbeit mit erfahrenem Videoteam in lockerer, produktiver Atmosphäre

Bewerbung:

Bitte sende uns bis asap Deine Bewerbung mit:
* 2–3 aktuellen Bildern oder Showreel
* Kurzprofil (Name, Alter, Standort)
* Optional: Link zu Instagram / Agenturseite / Eigenen Reels
* Betreff: „UGC-Videodreh Heidelberg – Vorname Nachname“

Bewerbung bitte per WhatsApp an: +49 172 7042469

(Phillip Kirillov - IMMO4.0 GmbH)

Hinweis:

Die finalen Produktionen erscheinen im Rahmen einer Online-Marketingkampagne für den Bereich Kapitalanlage-Immobilien. Seriös, hochwertig, glaubwürdig.

Wir freuen uns auf Deine Bewerbung – let’s create!

Dein Team von IMMO 4.0 GmbH

***PAID OPPORTUNITY* – OMG STORIES**

📢 Calling all storytellers, survivors, and secret-keepers…

Do you have a jaw-dropping story that no one believes actually happened?

Something wild, shocking, or totally unforgettable?

We’re filming a brand-new series for the hit YouTube channel OMG Stories **(450k)** , where real people share the most unbelievable things they’ve ever been through - from insane twists of fate to dark secrets, betrayals, and life-changing moments.

🎥 This is a PAID opportunity and filming happens in a London studio.

If that sounds like you (or someone you know), get in touch!

📧 Send your story to **[mireille.lee@upstream-media.co.uk](mailto:mireille.lee@upstream-media.co.uk)**

https://www.youtube.com/@OMG_stories

🚨URGENT CASTING CALL🚨

Project Title: SIO: Origins
Production Company: Museboxx M&F
Location: Darbyshire???? TBA (UK-based production)
Deadline: Urgent

Role: Co-Starring Leads – Names TBA
We’re casting for two dynamic male actors to take on a co-starring leading roles in our upcoming production, SIO: Origins, part of the larger SIO universe. The roles are emotionally charged and physically demanding, featuring performance across acting, dance, singing, and occasional stunt choreography. For these roles, We do have places for the characters to appear on the final episode of SIO:Echoes of the SIX - which has been airing throughout this year online. And to be a part of other SIO series', including live performances and other Muaeboxx projects.

Character Traits & Requirements:

• Sexuality: Gay & Bisexual
• Age: 26-28
• Height: 5ft 7 to 6ft
• Performance Abilities: Singer, Dancer, Acting and Rap
• Comfortable of doing own Stunts
• Comfortable with doing Gymnastics
• No piercings/jewelry

• Must be available for Live Performances

Previous experience in emotionally intense roles is a bonus

Payment & Contract:
Budget is currently being finalised. Payment details will be discussed at a later stage and confirmed in actor contracts. This will be a credited role with potential for expanded involvement in future series.

To Apply:
Send an email to museboxxmfcasting@gmail.com to send the following: Submit headshot, showreel (if available).
Audition scripts and details will be provided upon application.

If you have any issues with contacting the email above, please don't hesitate to contact our other email below - wintersxperia@gmail.com

More details about the projects will be discussed throughout the Audition process.

• Comfortable with doing Gymnastics
• No piercings/jewelry

• Must be available for Live Performances

Previous experience in emotionally intense roles is a bonus

Payment & Contract:
Budget is currently being finalised. Payment details will be discussed at a later stage and confirmed in actor contracts. This will be a credited role with potential for expanded involvement in future series.

To Apply:
Send an email to museboxxmfcasting@gmail.com to send the following: Submit headshot, showreel (if available).
Audition scripts and details will be provided upon application.

If you have any issues with contacting the email above, please don't hesitate to contact our other email below - wintersxperia@gmail.com

More details about the projects will be discussed throughout the Audition process.

items.text: Hello, group! My name is Scott, and I work for an award-winning production company that is developing a new documentary series focused on couples in which one of the members was couch surfing, living out of their van, staying with family, or unhoused when the relationship started. We hope to show the world that everyone deserves love, regardless of their living circumstances. If this applies to you, please see the casting notice below. This is a paid opportunity if selected.

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of one or more people, people standing, heart, poster, magazine and text that says 'AN AWARD- RD-WINNING PRODUCTION COMPANY IS NOW CASTING COUPLES IN WHICH ONE OF THE PEOPLE WAS UNHOUSED WHEN THE RELATIONSHIP STARTED, YET LOVE STILL PREVAILED. THIS COULD BE YOUR CHANCE to SHARE YOUR STORY! IF IFYOUARE: YOU ARE: DATING IN A LONG-TERM -TERM RELATIONSHIP ENGAGED MARRIED AND EITHER PERSON IN THE RELATIONSHIP WAS LIVING IN SHELTERS, VEHICLE, OR IN-AND-OUT OF FAMILY MEMBERS HOMES WHEN YOU FIRST MET,WE WANT TO HEAR FROM YOU! To apply, please Ao to: https://risis.sganacc .castingcrane.com/ Must be 18+ and legal U.S. resident. See site for full eligibility. We encourage applicants of all backgrounds and experience'

We’re SUPER excited to be opening our books! Please ensure you read ALL the info below before applying!

📌 We are only accepting applications from UK based people

📌 We welcome all ages, genders and ethnicities
 
📌We are a sole representative agency

📌 Are you able to travel and be flexible? We often have last minute requests for self tapes or in person castings, please only apply if you can commit

Please tag a friend, share and drop any questions below!! ⬇️

items.text:
The Core Theatre in Richardson is auditioning for The Trial of Ebeneezer Scrooge.
Directed by Staci Ingram
Show runs December 5 -December 21 / Industry Nite: December 15
Written by Mark Brown
A year after his miraculous transformation, Ebenezer Scrooge is back to his old ways and is suing Jacob Marley and the Ghosts of Christmas Past, Present and Future for breaking and entering, kidnapping, slander, pain and suffering, attempted murder and the intentional infliction of emotional distress.
Rehearsals will start in October and be Saturday afternoons, Sunday-Wed evenings.  There are tons of great character roles with minimal stage time allowing for flexibility in rehearsal schedule.
All Roles Available.
Auditions will consist of cold readings from the script.
 
Judge Stanchfield R. Pearson -Male 40's-60s Frustrated Magistrate
Solomon Rothschild-Male 20's-50s Jolly Solicitor
Ebenezer Scrooge-Male 40's-60s Miser
Bailiff- Male 20's-50's Hardworking under appreciated Bailiff
Bob Cratchit-Male 30's-50s Hardworking Clerk
Mrs. Cratchit-Female 30's-50s Bobs Outspoken wife (*cameo role)
Fred- Male 20's-40's Scrooge's Jolly Nephew 
Sara Wainwright- Female 20's-60's Wealthy but charitable woman
Jacob Marley- Male 40's-60s Scrooges former Partner
Ghost of Christmas Past- (Open) innocent but wise 
Fan- Female appears teenaged Scrooges younger sister (*Cameo Role)
Belle- Female 20's-50's Scrooges former love
Mrs. Dilber- Female any age Theif and flirt
Ghost of Christmas Yet to Come- Any age/gender no lines
The Translator - Any age/gender translates what Ghost of Christmas yet to come says

items.text:
Hello, Actors!!

My name is Colin Neufeld, and I am a talent representative for actors of Film & Television at JL Model Talent Management in Vancouver, British Columbia. I am currently expanding my roster and looking for awesome people for my team.

I am open to experienced actors and actors new to the business, so long as you consider yourself an actor first and foremost! (And hopefully you love every aspect of the Biz—it REALLY helps!)

Availability and flexibility are a must. Please only apply if you are

willing to make the time commitment that it requires to pursue a career in this field. If you are new to the industry and wish to apply, I am happy to consider you so long as you have attended, or are attending, actor training (either in person or online).

I am looking for people with great attitudes who want to do cool things with other awesome people. That is basically what the whole gig is about.

To get started with your application we need a few materials: 

1. A Professional Headshot: Please attach a high-quality professional headshot. 

2. Your acting resume

3. Self Tape Slate: should include the following segments:

   - Slate: Start your recording by introducing yourself confidently, mentioning your name, height, where you live and 1 interesting fact about yourself. Please keep this under 30 seconds.

 

4. Self Tape Film 

 -Demo Tape OR Dramatic Monologue or Scene: Choose a monologue or scene that best demonstrates your dramatic abilities, keeping it under 1 minute. If you have a scene from a recent acting class please submit it here.

When submitting your files, please label them in this format:

NAME - APPLICATION - JLMODELTALENTMANAGEMENT

Please email me at [Colin@jlmtm.com](mailto:Colin@jlmtm.com) with your materials . I will be contacting selected performers for interviews in the next couple of weeks.

Cheers!

Colin

items.text:
VI SØGER EN HISTORIE DER HAR BETYDNING FOR DIG

Vi er i gang med et dokumentarprojekt på efterskolen for scenekunst, og vi søger en person, der har en hjerteskærende eller personlig historie med stor betydning – noget du har lyst til at fortælle videre.

Vi vil lave en lille dokumentarfilm om dig og din oplevelse, og hvordan den har påvirket dit liv.

Efterskolen ligger tæt på Aarhus, så transport er nemt.

Kunne det interessere dig, må du meget gerne sende en besked og kort fortælle om din historie – eller ringe til os på **42903942**.

Mvh Ida og Danaya🙂

topComments.text: Lyder mega spændene! Jeg er også interesseret😊
Jeg vil gerne hjælpe jer men jeg har ikke tid til at skrive lige nu.

items.text:
Har lige nu flere filmproduktioner, hvor der er brug for statister..
Søger folk inden for 60 minutters kørsel fra Århus.

#1
Uge 40 - Reklamefilm Østjylland

Location: Malling

Søger: Mand + Kvinde i alderen 55-65 år. Skal spille et modent par. Kan søges individuelt - men privat relation foretrækkes.

Søger: Ung familie (Far, mor + barn ca 5 år). Skal have relation.

Tid: 1/2 dag

Lønnet

#2
November - reklamefilm Norden

Location: Østjylland

Søger: Alle typer (skal bruge 10-15 personer) - med mod og lyst til statistrolle + at danse simpel koreografi i rollen. Danseerfaring er ikke et krav .

Søger: Gymnaster/showdansere/HipHop alder 16-40 år, der skal lave mere kompliceret koreografi. Gerne en dansegruppe (mix M/K), der kender hinanden

Tid: 1-2 optagedage

Lønnet

Send besked til kontakt@kaiserwetter.dk med note om hvilken rolle du søger, foto, navn, alder og hvor i Jylland du bor.

topComments.text: Hvorfor vælger du at være anonym?
Har sendt dig en mail 🤗

items.text:
**Paid Studio Gig – Surrey, BC (1–2 days, max 7 hrs/day)**

Hey Vancouver actors! We’re producing a batch of short videos for our brand (YouTube, Reels, TikTok, Facebook) and are looking for a confident on-camera presenter to record with us at our Surrey studio.

**What it is:**
* 1–2 studio days, max **7 hours per day**
* Scripted teleprompter reads + a few simple pickups/B-roll
* We provide the studio, teleprompter, and all gear
* **Contract provided** and **payment in full on wrap**

**You:** Comfortable on camera, friendly, clear delivery, can self-report to Surrey.

**Dates/Rate:** negotiable and flexable 

If you’re interested, please fill out this form, https://form.jotform.com/252610493666057 

with:
* Headshot + reel/links
* Your availability in **[date range]**
* A quick note confirming you can get to Surrey

Thanks! Excited to meet some local talent.

items.text:
Hej! 

Zaczynamy casting do reklamy i poszukuję następujących postaci. 

SZUKMAY: 

1.Chłopiec: 10-12 lat, smutne oczy, szczupły, uzdolniony tanecznie - szukamy chłopców uzdolnionych tanecznie. Adeptów szkół tanecznych, gimnastycznych, baletowych. 

2.Mama:  ok 40 lat. Życie pchnęło ją do roli tej twardej, ale na ekranie widzimy, jak emocjonalną i kochającą matka jest dla bohatera.

4.Komisja egzaminacyjna: 4 osoby, zróżnicowane wiekowo, tancerze, surowe twarze, piękne sylwetki. Wiek - 30- 60 lat - nie muszą tańczyć ale muszą mieć sylwetki wiarygodne do roli byłych tancerzy 

5.Koledzy i koleżanki Chłopca: demokratyczna reprezentacja grupy rówieśniczej bohatera.- wiek 10-12 lat  - te dzieci tez będą musiały tańczyć i powtórzyć choreografię, więc super jeśli mają doświadczenie taneczne. 
1. Tancerz dubler - dubler naszego 10-12 letniego chłopca

2.Mama:  ok 40 lat. Życie pchnęło ją do roli tej twardej, ale na ekranie widzimy, jak emocjonalną i kochającą matka jest dla bohatera.

message.text:
🔥 No son reliquias. No es pasado.
Es fuerza, ritmo y energía que siguen latiendo.
Lo que hacemos no es una pieza de museo. Es danza viva.

Tomamos la fuerza del gaucho —su energía, su destreza, su presencia—
y la llevamos a un escenario con una propuesta estética cuidada y contemporánea.

💥 Que suenen los bombos, que vibren las boleadoras, que estalle la danza.
@millennialgaucho.ok 

#danza #malambo #boleadoras #latigos #argentina

Vi søger rigtige relationer til en reklamefilm der skal optages i Århus eller Billund, jobbet er godt lønnet. Forventet optagedag er  d. 8. eller 9. okt.

 
* to ældre veninder (65 år – skal tale med jysk dialekt)
* far og søn (far 35-40, søn ca 6 – 7 år – skal lyde sjællandsk)
* to unge venner (20-22 år, kan komme alle steder fra )

 

 

Send billede og info med navn, alder og hvor du bor til [info@kielcasting.com](mailto:info@kielcasting.com)

🎭✨ Vil du være med bag kulisserne på et stort musicalprojekt i Skive?

Musikteater Skive søger lige nu frivillige og praktikanter til oktober forestilling ‘An Ideal American’.
👉 Vi har især brug for en assistent til instruktøren (regi) – en unik chance for at lære teaterarbejdet indefra og få praktisk erfaring med opsætning af en professionel produktion.

Vi lover et kreativt fællesskab, masser af nye kontakter og oplevelser, du kan bruge i dit CV eller studie.

🔹 Er du interesseret? Skriv hurigt til os her på Facebook eller på mail: formand@musikteaterskive.dk

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig – og vi har brug for dig NU! 💡

sharedPost.text:
🎭 CASTING DO MUSICALU „CIENIE” 🎶

Szukamy młodych, śpiewających aktorów do zespołu wokalno-aktorskiego nowego musicalu „CIENIE”, którego prapremiera odbędzie się 13.12.2025 w Łodzi! 

Projekt kierowany jest do młodych adeptów sztuki scenicznej (od 16 roku życia).

👉 Aby wziąć udział w castingu, należy przesłać selftape wraz z nagraniem krótkiej piosenki (ok. 1,5 min.).

📩 Zgłoszenia przyjmujemy do 20.09.2025 na adres: musicalcienie@gmail.com

Tylko wybrane osoby zostaną zaproszone na casting stacjonarny, który odbędzie się 27.09.2025 w Łodzi.

🔹 Reżyseria i inscenizacja: Antoniusz Dietzius
🔹 Choreografia: Antonina Grupińska

📅 Terminy prób:
15.10 – 04.12.2025 (czwartki–niedziele)
05.12 – 12.12.2025 (próby całodniowe)

🎟️ Spektakle: 13–19.12.2025

💰 Udział w projekcie płatny.

✨ Nie przegap okazji, aby dołączyć do niezwykłego projektu musicalowego! ✨

📌 Informacja o ochronie danych osobowych:
Przesyłając zgłoszenie, wyrażasz zgodę na przetwarzanie swoich danych osobowych wyłącznie w celu organizacji castingu do musicalu „Cienie”, zgodnie z przepisami RODO. Dane nie będą udostępniane podmiotom trzecim i zostaną usunięte po zakończeniu procesu rekrutacji.

🎬 Casting Call – Mr. Fix It: The Joe Grind Story
Romantic comedy about a kindhearted handyman who finds himself in playful mischief.

📍 Filming in the Greater Toronto Area
💰 Paid roles ($150–$250/day)
🎭 Non-union production
📅 Must be available October 24, 25 & 26
🗓 Deadline to apply: September 25th

Roles:
✨ Marley – Black female lead, strong, witty, intelligent
✨ Mrs. Graydon – Female, open ethnicity, 25–45
✨ Mrs. Johnson – Female, open ethnicity, 25–45
✨ Mrs. Slaunwhite – Female, open ethnicity, 25–45

📩 Submit headshot & resume to TheJoeGrindStory@gmail.com

items.text: Shailene Woodley („Big Little Lies“): “I think Tony is absolutely incredible and coming to class for me isn’t just about letting loose and growing my ability as an actor but more sometimes to really open up myself to the universe and just be. Sometimes I find him saying things that I mentally live by and its so refreshing to constantly hear them being affirmed. Thank you so much for every week re-instilling that positivity and creativity and openness within. You allow me as an actor to forget about the character and remember about Shailene, which makes every movement, moment and word so authentic and true. I’m so grateful to have you as a mentor.”

Gesucht: Bankett-Tänzerin für kreatives Projekt in Berlin

Für ein exklusives Fotoprojekt in Berlin suche ich eine erfahrene Bankett-Tänzerin, die bereits Auftritts- und Bühnenerfahrung mitbringt.

Anforderungen:

Erfahrung im Bereich Tanzperformance / Bankett-Tanz

Ausstrahlung, Ausdrucksstärke und Sicherheit im Auftreten

Verlässlichkeit und Professionalität beim Shooting

Projekt:
Das Shooting verbindet künstlerische Fotografie mit Tanzperformance und findet in Berlin statt. Ziel ist es, Eleganz, Bewegung und Atmosphäre in einzigartigen Bildern festzuhalten.

Ort & Zeit:
Berlin – Termin nach Absprache (Herbst 2025).

Honorar / Zusammenarbeit:
Nach Vereinbarung – gerne auf TFP- oder Honorar-Basis.

👉 Interessierte Tänzerinnen können sich mit kurzem Portfolio, Fotos oder Videos ihrer bisherigen Arbeit melden.

items.text:
CASTING MONOLOG – bei Interesse findet am 06. Und 07 November in Berlin – auf  der Probebühne ein Arbeiten mir statt. Bitte melden per e-mail oder Nachricht!

Musik - Schwenk auf ein Sofa oder Bett. Die Schauspielerin erhebt sich aufreizend lächelnd:

*Meine Herren – Ihr Mächtigen dieser Erde – ein jeder Mann erwartet sich ein Fest … mit mir…*

Musik - Überblendung

Die SCHAUSPIELERIN, in einem dünnen seidenen Negligé gekleidet, in ihrer Künstlergarderobe – sie schminkt sich, betrachtet die Papierkrone, die auf dem Schminktisch liegt: …..*ja ja*….*mit mir…*

Die SCHAUSPIELERIN schenkt sich einen Schluck Vodka ein, raucht eine Zigarette zu Ende.  Die SCHAUSPIELERIN betrachtet sich lange im Spiegel – Tränen in den Augen:

*… und…die Mächtigen dieser Erde waschen verlogen ihre Hände in Unschuld …..Wir haben es nicht gewollt. Eine bitterböse Ironie“*

Musik Ende – Überblendung. Die SCHAUSPIELERIN geht einen langen dunklen Gang entlang. An der einen Wand Bilder von Mächtigen Männer: Trump, Putin, Xi, Ghandi, Hitler, Ben Gurion, usw. Auf der anderen Gangseite Bilder von bekannten Frauen der Weltgeschichte. Musik - Überblendung auf leere Bühne – Die SCHAUSPIELERIN in einem bodenlangen Mantel, auf dem Kopf die goldene Papierkrone, grell geschminkt, stark rote Lippen, weißumrandete Augen - in einem Lichtkegel:

*…doch gebt mir ein Königreich als Bühne, Prinzen für die Schauspieler – und ein Haus voller Monarchen! Wie stellt man sonst einen so stolzen Vorwurf dar, wie die Geschichte von Euch - Mächtigen? Meine Herren - Verzeiht – wenn Ihr es schafft, dass schon ein kleiner Tintenklecks auf einem bloßen Stück Papier den Wert einer Million bestimmen kann – so lasst uns fadenscheinige Komödianten für heute den verwegenen Versuch, als Nullen der gewaltigen Totale auf eure Fantasie zu wirken!*

Musik - Überblendung

Die SCHAUSPIELERIN:

*Ja - mit Eurer Fantasie stellt Euch Armeen vor! Und macht aus einem Manne tausend! Doch wenn ich „Pferde“ sage, seht sie, Seht! Da sind sie! Seht sie traben, diese Pferde! Seht ihre Hufe in die weiche Erde schlagen!*

*Meine Herren - nur eure Gedanken sind´s, die meine Könige in Gold und Purpur kleiden müssen, sie hin und her versetzen. Nur Eure Fantasie springt über Zeiten weg und kann den Lauf von Jahren umdrehen, wie ein Stundenglas.*

*Bildet Euch ein, da wären tausend Schiffe! Und seht wie mächtig ihre Brust sich durch den stolzen Schaum des Meeres bricht, vom unsichtbaren Wind gejagt!*

*Und seht den flinken Burschen dort mit seiner Lunte!*

*Jetzt zündet er die teuflische Kanone- und alles bricht vor Euch zusammen!*

*Und weiter! Versetzt euch wie ein Blitz aufs Schlachtfeld!*

*Seht meine Schwerter tanzen und sich in eurer Feinde Brust versenken!*

*Ja, sie sind aus Blech und schadhaft, lächerlich. Aber sie tanzen nicht zum Spaß: die Schlacht ist ernst, wahrhafter als die Wirklichkeit! Ich bitte aber den Historiker unter Ihnen – in aller Demut - die Daten, Zahlen und die Fakten nicht mit dem Maßstab der exakten Wissenschaft zu messen. Die Geschichte von Euch mächtigen Herren lässt sich nicht erzählen.  Nur in ihrer Ganzheit ist sie wahr, und wo sie wahr ist, ist sie nicht exakt! Denn nichts erhebt sich von der Erde, dass nicht die Zeit mit ihrer Sichel niedermäht! Im Gegenteil……ich baut vor Eurer Tür ein Weidenhüttchen und sänge Lieder – laut - der Liebe! Und wenn die Musik der Liebe Nahrung - so spiel ich weiter, weiter bis zum Überdruss. Meine Herren - Ihr Mächtigen dieser Erde: Schießt nicht auf mich Komödiantin!*

Mit einem Lächeln verbeugt sich die SCHAUSPIELERIN – dann plötzlich ein Schuss.  Die SCHAUSPIELERIN sinkt langsam zu Boden. Blackout.

items.text:
Ich suche 1-3 Mitstreiter für ein Straßentheaterprojekt, egal ob Anfänger, erfahrene Amateure oder Profis.

Das Stück (zwischen 2:30 und 15:00 Minuten) soll gemeinsam anhand unserer individuellen Fähigkeiten (zB Tanz, Musik, Akrobatik) entwickelt werden. Grobe Konzepte habe ich schon erarbeitet, genau so wie ich schon einen rechtlichen Rahmen abgeklärt habe.

Mir ist dabei wichtig, dass es humorvoll zugeht, Gag auf Gag wäre ein zentraler Punkt meines Vorstellung, gern gepaart mit einer anachronistischen Optik.

Erfahrung und Möglichkeit im Bereich Bühnenbau und technischer Umsetzung ist reichlich vorhanden.

Ihr solltet in der Umgebung von Aachen wohnen, um regelmässige Proben möglich zu machen.

Neben dem Interesse am Spielen möchte ich den finanziellen Aspekt nicht ganz aussen vor lassen, ich könnte mir langfristig vorstellen, hier einen relevanten Teil meines Einkommens zu bestreiten. Ziel ist zunächst das guerilliamässige Auftreten in Fußgängerzonen, später auch die Teilnahme an internationalen Festivals in Deutschland, Belgien und Frankreich.

Das Ganze soll wirklich langfristig angelegt sein, gern über mehrere Jahre.

Die Fotos habe ich mal angehängt, um ganz grob zu zeigen, in welche Richtung es gehen könnte.

Ich freue mich über alle Anfragen.

Hello all, this is another post for a different student film happening on Auraria Campus. I am not involved in this one, I am posting to this group for the producer since he is not on Facebook. So if you are interested in this one please contact the producer. 

Producer- Brennan Jones bjones89@msudenver.edu 

Production Title- The Cost of Greed 

Production Dates- Exact dates are not set but filming will be in October 

Logline- Peter and Henry are sent on a treasure hunt to a house that is believed to be abandoned. Where they then discover it's not a treasure hunt after all and they must face their greed. Either take the treasure or leave empty handed. 

Peter (19-25) Male 

Peter has a moral compass that he deals with during this film. He wants to do the right thing and in the end that pays off for him. 

Henry (19-25) Male 

Henry is a billionaire with no need for more money, however that does not stop him from thinking he needs more. He is corrupt and in the end karma gets to him. 

Audition Dates- September 18th-September 29th

Audition Location- Email-Self Tape

This is a student film for a final project therefore this film is non paid and non union.

Contact Email- bjones89@msudenver.edu 

Must contact the producer to be consider for the role. Once you contact Brennan he will send you the audition material.

items.text:
Hello, we are currently casting for a student film on Auraria Campus! 

Producers- Isabella Coronado & Alanagh Finken 

Production Title- Normal Activity 

Production Dates- We don't have exact dates yet but we do know that we are filming in October. 

Logline- A mocumentary following a college's ghost hunting group as they prepare to explore a haunted local brewery's basement where a spirit has resided for the past thirty years. 

Alex (19-25) Male 

Alex is the leader of the ghost hunting group, he is very enthusiastic. He is clearly the one that is most devoted to this group. 

Chelsea (19-25) Female 

Chelsea is your typical girly girl likes being on camera but does not care about the club she is in. She is pretending to so that the club can get funding for the "haunted (not haunted) hot springs". 

Tommy (19-25) Male 

Tommy is very clearly apart of the club because he has eyes for Chelsea, he could not care less otherwise. 

Vera (19-25) Female 

Vera is Alex's sister and is only there because Alex believes they needed a fourth member and basically bribed Vera to join by saying she could borrow his car whenever she wants. 

Gary (45-55) Male 

Gary is the nightwatchmen for the brewery basement. He is very encouraging to Alex with his ghost hunting group. However that encouragement is not for reasons you think, Gary has a secret. 

Documentarian (20-30) Male, Female, Non Binary 

The documentarian is not really shown on camera, however they play a very important role. They are the voice we hear throughout the film asking questions to our characters, and making sarcastic and humorous remarks because they like everyone except Alex, thinks this club is utterly ridicules. 

Audition Dates- September 18th-September 29th 

Audition Location- Email-Self Tape 

This is a student film for a final project therefore this film is non paid and non union. 

**Contact Email- afinken1@msudenver.edu | icoronad@msudenver.edu **

**You must email both producers. Email the producers about your interest in the role and then we will send you the audition piece for your self tape. You must email to be considered, Facebook Messages does not count. **

Casting Call – Mandlig skuespiller/statist søges

Vi er et hold på seks studerende fra VIA Film & Transmedia i Aarhus. I forbindelse med et skoleprojekt samarbejder vi med designer Fie Nielsen og hendes studie, Fjör Studio, om branding af en ny tøjkollektion.

Kollektionen udforsker, hvad det vil sige at være mand i dag, og leger med udtryk, der udfordrer de traditionelle forestillinger om styrke, følelser og identitet.

Vi søger en mand i alderen 17–30 år, ca. 180 cm høj, almindelig af bygning og med tøjstørrelse small–medium.

Praktisk info
 Optagelserne finder sted i Skanderborg
 Mandag den 22/9
 Kl. 09.00–17.00

Projektet er frivilligt, men vi sørger selvfølgelig for mad, drikke, transport – og en sjov oplevelse samt muligheden for at få et spændende projekt på CV’et.

Kontakt Fredrik på (+45) 2285 1519 eller 354549@via.dk, hvis du er interesseret. 

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig!

Casting Call – Voice Actors (Ulønnet)

Hej alle,

Vi er et hold fra Masterclass på Potemkin – Den Jyske Filmskole, som er i postproduktion på et spændende projekt. Derfor søger vi nu stemmeskuespillere til to roller.

Logline:

En håbefuld, men overset filminstruktør får chancen i en branche styret af sequels og profit – og må vælge mellem at gå på kompromis med sine værdier eller med sin karriere.

Vi søger:

 • Kvindestemme – til at udlevere en Robertpris (kort ceremoniel replik - tænk "And the Oscar goes to..."). Alder er underordnet.

 • Mandestemme – til rollen som producer (kort telefondialogscene). Alder underordnet, da det er stemmen vi søger, men vi søger i omfanget af 25-39 år. 

Praktisk:

 • Projektet er ulønnet, men alle medvirkende bliver krediteret i filmen.
        • Lydoptagelsen vil foregå i Potemkins lydstudie på Fredens Torv 3A, Aarhus C 8000.

Er du interesseret? Send mig en mail på simonthomaslange@gmail.com med en kort besked, eventuelt som lydoptaglese, så får du flere detaljer :)

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig!

LOOKING FOR 2 MEN (preferably BASS or BARITONE), 1 WOMAN (preferably ALTO) who can dance and have the ability to harmonize, for our upcoming Holiday Show. 

Ensemble Stage is a professional theater located in Banner Elk, NC which is situated in the Blue Ridge Mtns. in western North Carolina. Our facility consists of over 8000 sq. ft. which includes a 99-seat performance auditorium.

About 90 total hours (rehearsals + performances), no two-show days, no 10-out-of-12's, no more than 3 performances per week (7 total performances). 

contract runs 11/14 thru 12/20.  Fyi- we have no rehearsals Wednesday thru Saturday of Thanksgiving week so you have an opportunity to go be with family if you choose. 

Pay is $260 per week for five weeks (comes to around $14 per hour of actual rehearsal and performance time). Housing is fully provided(includes full kitchen, washer/dryer, wifi, free parking, individual bedroom, no more than two share a bathroom (but usually private) , etc.  Also, no smoking, and no pets (or service animals) are allowed in any housing. 

Round-trip travel reimbursed at $0.25 per mile

Finally,since we are located in the mountains, and since Ensemble Stage does not have a "company car" available for use, having your own vehicle while here is pretty much a necessity. There really is no such thing as walking to the store or to the theatre.

If interested please respond to info@ensemblestage.com, subject- CMAS AUDITIONS. I will then send you details and parameters for you to prepare a video callback audition to be submitted.

items.text:
Thank you so much for welcoming me to your group!  

I'm a NYC and NJ native, now living in Florida, pursuing acting work to support my film project.  I have significant experience in films.  Supported directors and producers.  I had 5 years as an extra for feature films such as El Cantante, Be Kind/Rewind, and traveled to audition for theatre and short films. Beyond acting, I'm an editor, photographer, and former Spectrum Television production intern with five years of hands-on experience with equipment, and in 2019 created my first show in Western Connecticut, Channel 192, "Spoken Voices."  A passionate advocate against domestic violence. I bring dedication, creativity, and authenticity to every role, and you can find me on FaceBook, "Maribel Brooks" for future auditioning!
